content: Ed-Marcavage: Merged two substantial documentation-focused PRs: #1675 "Agentic Eliza Plugin Documenter - Multilingual" (+43,511/-16,747 lines) and #1993 "Optimizes Technical Docs for LLMs & Vectorization" (+28,851/-9,849 lines). Currently has one open PR (#2419) addressing missing documentation in a plugin's README. Made significant code changes across 1,378 files (+152,646/-25,528 lines) through 43 commits, with work split between feature development (51%) and documentation improvements (33%).
